column2: SELECT SpecObj.plate, SpecObj.mjd, SpecObj.fiberID, GalSpecLine.oiii_#_flux, GalSpecLine.oiii_#_cont,GalSpecLine.oiii_#_eqw,GalSpecLine.h_delta_eqw, GalSpecLine.sigma_balmer FROM SpecObj JOIN GalSpecLine ON SpecObj.specobjid = GalSpecLine.specobjid WHERE h_beta_eqw < # AND oiii_#_eqw < # AND sigma_balmer > # AND SpecObj.class = &&& AND SpecObj.z between # and # AND SpecObj.snmedian_g >#
